## 🧪 Test Automation Workflow (Updated 2026-02-27)

**When user requests test run:**

1. **Immediate response:** "🚀 Test sedang berjalan. Saya akan kabari setelah selesai."
2. **Execute test:** Run command di background/foreground
3. **Follow up:** "✅ Test selesai! Berikut hasilnya:" + summary

**Why this matters:**
- User tahu test sedang berjalan (tidak hanging)
- User tahu akan dikabari setelah selesai
- User tidak perlu menunggu di WhatsApp (bisa buka yang lain)

**Example responses:**
- "🚀 Login test sedang berjalan. Saya akan kabari setelah selesai."
- "🚀 Sales test sedang berjalan (3 scenarios). Saya akan kabari setelah selesai."

**Note: NO time estimation** — depends on internet/server load, can be misleading.

---

## ⚠️ Lesson Learned: Always Send Test Results (2026-02-27)

**Incident:**
- User requested "run sales" test
- Test completed successfully (~10 min)
- WhatsApp disconnected/reconnected during execution
- Agent forgot to send results to user
- User had to ask: "kok hasil test nya gak ada?"

**Root Cause:**
- Agent started test but didn't follow up after completion
- Disconnect caused context gap
- No mechanism to ensure results are always sent

**Fix Applied:**
- Updated TOOLS.md with "Critical: ALWAYS Send Results" section
- Added instruction to check process status even after disconnect
- Must parse results from exit code, videos, screenshots

**Prevention:**
- After test completes, IMMEDIATELY send results
- Check `videos/` and `screenshots/` for latest files
- Parse pass/fail from file timestamps and names
- Never assume user knows test completed

